products.name: Green Run Star Hike Hi Sneakers
products.desc: High-top canvas sneakers in green. Round rubber cap toe. Lace-up closure in white. Eyelet vents and logo printed at inner side. Webbing pull-loop at heel collar. Tonal webbing trim at heel. Black stripe at welt. Foam rubber midsole in white featuring rubberized logo at heel. Treaded rubber outsole in white and tan. Silver-tone hardware. Approx. 1.5
